==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bā qiān lǐ lù yún hé yuè

===Etymology===
Literally: The moon and clouds of 8,000 [[里|li]].

===Idiom===
# Describes the great distances involved in a military campaign.
# To travel far and wide.

